{"word":"G298 - ἀμώμητος - amṓmētos - am-o'-may-tos - Blameless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμώμητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">amṓmētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-o'-may-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Blameless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றமில்லாத, பிழையில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that cannot be censured, blameless"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3469 - μωμάομαι - mōmáomai - mo-mah'-om-ahee/3469\">G3469</a>; <i>unblameable:</i> - blameless.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G298/298\">G298</a>, <a href=\"#/G299/299\">G299</a>, <a href=\"#/G3469/3469\">G3469</a>, <a href=\"#/G3470/3470\">G3470</a>"}]}